- Bye-bye.

91
00:05:39,607 --> 00:05:41,041
I'll get going now.

92
00:05:41,041 --> 00:05:41,842
Be safe.

93
00:05:41,842 --> 00:05:43,233
Bye-bye.

94
00:05:43,233 --> 00:05:44,444
Bye.

95
00:05:50,453 --> 00:05:52,152
