important moments?

97
00:05:55,590 --> 00:06:00,469
Bro, you can't wait
for the Christmas party too, right?

98
00:06:02,444 --> 00:06:03,496
Right.

99
00:06:04,865 --> 00:06:05,999
I can't wait.

100
00:06:21,667 --> 00:06:23,049
