00:07:34,482 --> 00:07:36,323
Just a little more.

115
00:07:46,691 --> 00:07:49,002
Then, tomorrow,
I'll go there in the late afternoon.

116
00:07:49,088 --> 00:07:50,503
Okay, got it.

117
00:07:50,769 --> 00:07:52,490
It might not be much,
but I'll make the food.

118
00:07:52,514 --> 00:07:53,440
Really?

119
00:07:53,464 --> 00:07:56,998
Even though I said that,
I can only start preparing after work.

120
00:07:57,022 --> 00:07:58,511
Don't expect too much.

121
00:07:58,590 --> 00:08:00,293
I really can't wait.

122
00:08:01,230 --> 00:08:01,915
Okay.

123
00:08:01,939 --> 00:08:03,939
Yukata.

124
00:08:04,624 --> 00:08:07,420
I already brushed my teeth

125
00:08:07,506 --> 00:08:09,556
and cleaned my room.

126
00:08:09,931 --> 00:08:11,324
Aren't I a good boy?

127
00:08:11,683 --> 00:08:13,752
Yes, you're a good boy, Tane.

128
00:08:13,776 --> 00:08:14,995
But what's going on?

129
00:08:15,562 --> 00:08:16,730
It's Santa.

130
00:08:16,878 --> 00:08:17,731
Oh.

131
00:08:17,755 --> 00:08:19,499
Yukata, do you know?

132
00:08:19,624 --> 00:08:22,469
If you're not a good kid,
Santa won't come to see you.

133
00:08:22,515 --> 00:08:23,592
Of course, I know.

134
00:08:23,617 --> 00:08:27,607
I'm a good kid, so he will surely come.

135
00:08:27,631 --> 00:08:28,742
That's right.

136
00:08:28,898 --> 00:08:31,077
You're a good kid.
He'll definitely go see you.

137
00:08:31,101 --> 00:08:32,877
All right, it's time
for the good kid to go to bed.

138
00:08:32,877 --> 00:08:34,381
If you don't sleep soon,
Santa won't come, you know.

139
00:08:34,506 --> 00:08:35,515
He's not coming now.

140
00:08:36,987 --> 00:08:38,121
I'm going to bed.

141
00:08:39,673 --> 00:08:42,022
Yukata, good night.

142
00:08:42,046 --> 00:08:43,523
Yeah, good night.

143
00:08:47,409 --> 00:08:49,729
Lately, he's away been like that.

144
00:08:49,901 --> 00:08:52,399
If Santa could come every day,
that'd be great.

145
00:08:54,367 --> 00:08:55,009
Eh?

146
00:08:55,042 --> 00:08:56,777
Yutaka, what's wrong?

147
00:08:57,117 --> 00:08:57,611
Uh.

148
00:08:57,637 --> 00:08:59,939
No, nothing. See you tomorrow.

149
00:09:00,197 --> 00:09:02,197
Okay, good night.

150
00:09:30,574 --> 00:09:32,639
Yay! It's Santa!

151
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,573
He's up.

152
00:09:33,873 --> 00:09:34,841
He is up.

153
00:09:36,141 --> 00:09:38,211
Yay! It's Santa!

154
00:09:38,235 --> 00:09:40,115
Wow, that's great, Tane.

155
00:09:40,115 --> 00:09:41,748
- That's great.
- Right?

156
00:09:43,675 --> 00:09:44,517
Oh.

157
00:09:44,660 --> 00:09:46,362
He didn't come to see you?

158
00:09:46,410 --> 00:09:48,188
He doesn't come to see grownups.

159
00:09:48,765 --> 00:09:49,722
Why?

160
00:09:50,290 --> 00:09:52,158
Did you have a fight with Santa?

161
00:09:52,182 --> 00:09:53,093
Who would do that?

162
00:09:53,117 --> 00:09:55,117
Come on, Tane. Let's see what's inside.

163
00:09:55,141 --> 00:09:55,895
Okay.

164
00:09:56,165 --> 00:09:57,919
All right, I'm off to work.

165
00:09:57,943 --> 00:09:59,199
Okay, be safe.

166
00:10:04,959 --> 00:10:06,039
Hello?

167
00:10:07,477 --> 00:10:08,908
Sorry, Minoru.

168
00:10:08,979 --> 00:10:10,110
Huh? Yutaka?

169
00:10:10,134 --> 00:10:11,878
You sound weird.

170
00:10:12,316 --> 00:10:13,279
Are you okay?

171
00:10:13,553 --> 00:10:15,482
I don't think I'm okay.

172
00:10:16,155 --> 00:10:17,083
Huh?

173
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:43,943
Now, the plan is ruined.

174
00:11:00,822 --> 00:11:03,296
I really want to go to the party.

175
00:11:13,295 --> 00:11:14,897
In the end,

176
00:11:16,009 --> 00:11:20,079
even though I've grown up,
I still can't enjoy Christmas.

177
00:11:57,825 --> 00:11:59,059
Minoru...

178
00:11:59,633 --> 00:12:02,288
You didn't pick up my calls.
I thought you collapsed or something.

179
00:12:02,632 --> 00:12:03,403
Uh...

180
00:12:03,405 --> 00:12:05,080
Sorry, I was asleep.

181
00:12:05,416 --> 00:12:08,328
It's a relief that you're alive.

182
00:12:27,046 --> 00:12:29,015
Will Tane be okay?

183
00:12:29,742 --> 00:12:30,850
He's fine.

184
00:12:31,202 --> 00:12:34,621
Dad said he's so excited
and kept playing with the gift he got.

185
00:12:35,622 --> 00:12:36,856
Is that so?

186
00:12:37,684 --> 00:12:38,925
It's a relief

187
00:12:40,026 --> 00:12:42,595
that this doesn't turn into
an awful memory about Christmas.

188
00:12:44,982 --> 00:12:47,333
Don't worry about others.

189
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:49,168
Pay attention to yourself too.

190
00:12:53,337 --> 00:12:54,304
Here.

191
00:12:59,375 --> 00:13:00,313
Wow.

192
00:13:03,294 --> 00:13:04,670
Right.

193
00:13:04,717 --> 00:13:07,387
You said we have to eat udon when sick.

194
00:13:07,412 --> 00:13:08,124
Yeah.

195
00:13:08,248 --> 00:13:10,056
My mom's legendary udon.

196
00:13:10,642 --> 00:13:14,060
She'd chop up yuzu peel and put it
on the soft boiled udon noodles.

197
00:13:14,408 --> 00:13:15,528
Yuzu?

198
00:13:15,552 --> 00:13:16,401
Yeah.

199
00:13:16,463 --> 00:13:18,722
Back then, there was a
yuzu tree in the garden.

200
00:13:18,746 --> 00:13:20,333
So she'd pick some and put it in.

201
00:13:20,427 --> 00:13:22,001
But I just bought this.

202
00:13:23,269 --> 00:13:25,438
So, this is your mom's version.

203
00:13:25,907 --> 00:13:26,773
Yeah.

204
00:13:27,022 --> 00:13:28,508
My mom taught me.

205
00:13:32,747 --> 00:13:33,880
Please.

206
00:13:36,244 --> 00:13:38,007
Thank you for the food.

207
00:13:56,145 --> 00:13:57,303
It's delicious.

208
00:13:57,795 --> 00:13:59,305
The taste is very gentle.

209
00:14:00,506 --> 00:14:01,641
That's great.

210
00:14:03,965 --> 00:14:07,180
I'm glad I got to know
a lot of your mom's dishes.

211
00:14:08,983 --> 00:14:09,985
Is that so?

212
00:14:32,441 --> 00:14:35,074
I'll put fruit and yogurt in the fridge.
You should eat them later.

213
00:14:35,541 --> 00:14:36,576
Thank you.

214
00:14:44,584 --> 00:14:46,652
It's cold. You should put on a jacket.

215
00:14:47,044 --> 00:14:47,791
Oh.

216
00:14:47,817 --> 00:14:48,764
Sorry.

217
00:14:56,689 --> 00:14:57,497
Bye, then.

218
00:15:00,061 --> 00:15:01,968
Are you leaving now?

219
00:15:04,707 --> 00:15:05,473
Hmm?

220
00:15:05,919 --> 00:15:06,599
Uh.

221
00:15:06,625 --> 00:15:07,445
Sorry.

222
00:15:08,291 --> 00:15:10,009
I had to sleep here alone,

223
00:15:10,652 --> 00:15:12,845
so I got a little lonely.

224
00:15:23,165 --> 00:15:25,925
I'll stay with you
until you stop feeling lonely, then.

225
00:15:29,784 --> 00:15:30,797
Thank you.

226
00:15:37,873 --> 00:15:39,672
About the party, I'm really sorry.

227
00:15:41,586 --> 00:15:42,909
Don't worry about it.

228
00:15:43,278 --> 00:15:45,211
We can have another one
when you're better.

229
00:15:46,001 --> 00:15:46,846
But...

230
00:15:47,368 --> 00:15:49,916
It's Christmas, but because of me...

231
00:15:59,059 --> 00:16:00,026
Well.

232
00:16:01,430 --> 00:16:03,029
Can I tell you my story?

233
00:16:06,355 --> 00:16:07,099
Yeah.

234
00:16:18,864 --> 00:16:20,112
My mom

235
00:16:20,855 --> 00:16:22,748
died two years ago.

236
00:16:25,965 --> 00:16:28,020
Mom had always been weak,

237
00:16:28,176 --> 00:16:29,522
but after she gave birth to Tane,

238
00:16:29,658 --> 00:16:32,058
she was diagnosed with a serious
illness, and then passed away.

239
00:16:45,998 --> 00:16:48,475
Her baby is still so young.
I feel so sorry for her.

240
00:16:56,829 --> 00:16:58,751
Where is Mom?

241
00:17:03,783 --> 00:17:05,791
Tane, come here.

242
00:17:13,646 --> 00:17:17,336
We won't get to see Mom again.

243
00:17:22,756 --> 00:17:24,110
Never again.

244
00:17:33,166 --> 00:17:34,921
So that's how it was.

245
00:17:37,217 --> 00:17:39,392
I've never told you, right?

246
00:17:40,669 --> 00:17:42,461
I just want you to know.

247
00:17:47,047 --> 00:17:48,134
Thank you

248
00:17:48,249 --> 00:17:49,502
for telling me.

249
00:17:51,671 --> 00:17:54,707
We don't usually
get to be alone like this.

250
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:57,009
So,

251
00:17:57,044 --> 00:17:59,345
maybe it's good that
this Christmas turned out like this.

252
00:18:01,777 --> 00:18:02,527
Eh?

253
00:18:05,653 --> 00:18:07,653
I bought a small one
from the supermarket.

254
00:18:09,221 --> 00:18:10,690
It's so cute.

255
00:18:12,835 --> 00:18:14,160
It's an important day.

256
00:18:14,589 --> 00:18:16,635
Spending it with an important person

257
00:18:17,091 --> 00:18:18,531
