258
00:18:23,685 --> 00:18:24,870
Is that so?

259
00:18:26,918 --> 00:18:27,974
I see.

260
00:18:34,182 --> 00:18:35,114
I think...

261
00:18:35,617 --> 00:18:39,853
This is the first time I'm looking at a
Christmas tree with such a good feeling.

262
00:18:41,008 --> 00:18:42,221
Is that so?

263
00:18:42,688 --> 00:18:43,701
Yeah.

264
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:45,691
Actually,

265
00:18:45,861 --> 00:18:48,461
I've never liked Christmas.

266
00:18:53,158 --> 00:18:54,045
I think

267
00:18:54,058 --> 00:18:55,501
you must have...

268
00:18:56,063 --> 00:18:57,269
been through a lot of things too.

269
00:18:59,262 --> 00:19:01,262
I want to hear about it all.

270
00:19:03,911 --> 00:19:04,977
All of it?

271
00:19:05,507 --> 00:19:06,278
Yes.

272
00:19:09,048 --> 00:19:10,650
I want you to tell me everything.

273
00:19:11,692 --> 00:19:12,551
And I will...

274
00:19:13,401 --> 00:19:14,687
listen really well.

275
00:19:21,773 --> 00:19:23,021
Should I?

276
00:19:24,408 --> 00:19:25,112
Hmm?

277
00:19:27,333 --> 00:19:29,368
I've never thought about

278
00:19:30,603 --> 00:19:32,672
telling it to anyone.

279
00:19:34,567 --> 00:19:35,508
But...

280
00:19:37,456 --> 00:19:39,045
If it's Minoru...

281
00:20:20,620 --> 00:20:21,549
Hmm?

282
00:20:22,396 --> 00:20:24,557
Will Yukata be okay?

283
00:20:25,359 --> 00:20:28,861
